***CE Amplifier Design Using NgSpice***


Step 1:Create File
Open terminal: type command below 
nano ce_amp.cir

Step 2:In GNU Dashboard Paste below Script
* Common Emitter Amplifier

VCC vcc 0 DC 12
VIN in 0 SIN(0 0.01 1k)

R1 vcc base 100k
R2 base 0 22k

RC vcc collector 4.7k
RE emitter 0 1k

CIN in base 10u
COUT collector out 10u
CE emitter 0 100u

Q1 collector base emitter 2N3904

.model 2N3904 NPN(IS=6.734E-15 BF=255.9)

.tran 0.1ms 10ms
.control
run
plot v(in) v(out)
.endc

.end

Step 3:Run Simulation
ngspice ce_amp.cir

You can observe waveform and OutPut in Terminal.

